Dabao.

98
00:04:22,640 --> 00:04:23,760
Dabao.

99
00:04:23,760 --> 00:04:24,880
Where are you?

100
00:04:43,600 --> 00:04:45,320
Why did this painting fall off?

101
00:04:57,920 --> 00:05:00,040
Is the jade pendant on
the painting glowing?

102
00:05:02,360 --> 00:05:04,160
Am I drunk?

103
00:05:18,120 --> 00:05:22,000
♪Light up all the stars♪

104
00:05:22,520 --> 00:05:26,440
♪Wish for staying with you forever♪

105
